reviewText: Great footage and covers the London war experience from start to finish very infomratively and engagingly.
Excellent presentation, some completely new to us even though we are British. Highly recommend this DVD.
Great footage of London and its people which succeeds in capturing the steely spirit and resolve of a nation being bombarded by a ruthless enemy.  I would recommend this video to all WWII buffs.
Fascinating insight into what was really happening in London during the war
